\v 3 Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² me³-le⁴ Ni³na¹ nca³ coan⁴tsjao³, nca³ chja⁴ˀa²xin²-lao⁴³ yao³-no³ cjoa⁴cha³jnqui³.
